.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-UPTIME" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-uptime \- report node start time and uptime
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-uptime
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the node start timestamp and uptime in seconds from
.BR getinfo .
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"started_at":N,"uptime_seconds":N,"version":"..."}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-version (1),
.BR lightning-node-health (1)
